---
title: Cheesy Beef  Lentil Nachos with Lime Crema and Guac
description: Lentil 'nachos' are a quirky-fun combination of loaded tortillas scattered with all the classic toppings! Crispy, seasoned nachos are topped with mozzarella cheese, Mexican-inspired spiced lentils, tender beef and lime crema.
